name: PMX500
description: PMX500 (PMX) is a fully decentralized memecoin on PulseChain, launched with renounced ownership, permanently locked liquidity, and zero taxes. It has no intrinsic utility but serves as the PulseChain Memecoin 500 Index — a cultural symbol of belief, speculation, and meme culture. By design, its visibility and relevance grow alongside PulseChain, positioning PMX500 as a key beneficiary of the ecosystem’s success.
